    "rowsha": "AEtwCtNcx6wi22ou+b2N2xRRBomPvfCRSoNko8yiNYk=",
    "originContent": "# Django Shinobi - Fast Django REST Framework",
    "translatedContent": "# Django Shinobi - 빠른 Django REST 프레임워크"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "FKDSG5RJxO0nDVu6Ve7AylsfvJVLWyWlP2+D+2EPAP8=",
    "originContent": "[Documentation](https://pmdevita.github.io/django-shinobi)",
    "translatedContent": "[문서](https://pmdevita.github.io/django-shinobi)"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "42jEFDa6BT7eGJXcKRSjbVjC91thJBkLUwc68VLQdmA=",
    "originContent": "**Django Shinobi** is a web framework for building APIs with **Django** and Python 3.6+ **type hints**. ",
    "translatedContent": "**Django Shinobi**는 **Django**와 Python 3.6+ **타입 힌트**를 사용하여 API를 구축하기 위한 웹 프레임워크입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "FHi0PuzYbd2hitAiFVurlpk1EYnqhXYoEX/zpceeoUg=",
    "originContent": "It's a fork of the fantastic **[Django Ninja](https://github.com/vitalik/django-ninja)** library focused on ",
    "translatedContent": "이것은 훌륭한 **[Django Ninja](https://github.com/vitalik/django-ninja)** 라이브러리의 포크로,  "
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "uxVSV3vLgQJEHuju/2lu9Sxa3kYr7Pj2W4kM+U9a7Co=",
    "originContent": "community-desired features and fixes. Check out the list of [differences](https://pmdevita.github.io/django-shinobi/differences/) ",
    "translatedContent": "커뮤니티가 원하는 기능과 수정 사항에 초점을 맞추고 있습니다.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "XIfQKD084asnbt5sItIV8s1K0/K2BL0nSFgN3/ZFi8Y=",
    "originContent": "if you're coming from Ninja, as well as the [roadmap](https://github.com/pmdevita/django-shinobi/discussions/6)!",
    "translatedContent": "Ninja에서 오신 분들은 [차이점 목록](https://pmdevita.github.io/django-shinobi/differences/)과 [로드맵](https://github.com/pmdevita/django-shinobi/discussions/6)을 확인하세요!"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "KmmGRaXwKZE9f+3YyoPoqv9NhXh00BefTi6cFAKTFgE=",
    "originContent": " **Key features:**",
    "translatedContent": " **주요 특징:**"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "hvTX5qscrmCFvtFWIX4di7e8Gk9idG2EeWp4IlLVs4k=",
    "originContent": "  - **Easy**: Designed to be easy to use and intuitive.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **쉬움**: 사용하기 쉽고 직관적으로 설계되었습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "ul1lg4XAzoaQ8hHt1DHer6Xh4mR50p+whLRus7865N4=",
    "originContent": "  - **FAST execution**: Very high performance thanks to **<a href=\"https://pydantic-docs.helpmanual.io\" target=\"_blank\">Pydantic</a>** and **<a href=\"/docs/docs/guides/async-support.md\">async support</a>**.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **빠른 실행**: **<a href=\"https://pydantic-docs.helpmanual.io\" target=\"_blank\">Pydantic</a>**과 **<a href=\"/docs/docs/guides/async-support.md\">비동기 지원</a>** 덕분에 매우 높은 성능을 자랑합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "dbj4lCw2630PR5jytYbh+Vg35Xcx2WRjbIyITl4krGQ=",
    "originContent": "  - **Fast to code**: Type hints and automatic docs lets you focus only on business logic.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **빠른 코딩**: 타입 힌트와 자동 문서화로 비즈니스 로직에만 집중할 수 있습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "S6dC8mhKrBt8eMQcRqh/PJS6FVL/Rdi+3HhUjtMvlBA=",
    "originContent": "  - **Standards-based**: Based on the open standards for APIs: **OpenAPI** (previously known as Swagger) and **JSON Schema**.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **표준 기반**: API를 위한 공개 표준인 **OpenAPI** (이전 명칭 Swagger)와 **JSON Schema**를 기반으로 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "KX7g8zg4gF9I3F3yonGaQYoYDaPjRk1WmBUHpGiFA1o=",
    "originContent": "  - **Django friendly**: (obviously) has good integration with the Django core and ORM.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **Django 친화적**: (당연히) Django 코어 및 ORM과 좋은 통합성을 가집니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "/dm3ZTkomRe2lPnA25YGF0gW2xRore3nBX2MFoeS2mw=",
    "originContent": "  - **Production ready**: The original Ninja project is used by multiple companies on live projects.",
    "translatedContent": "  - **프로덕션 준비 완료**: 원래 Ninja 프로젝트는 여러 기업의 라이브 프로젝트에서 사용되고 있습니다."
  },
